<subSubSection box="[199,1436,1248,1273]" pageId="14" pageNumber="215" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1437,151,1273]" box="[199,1436,1248,1273]" pageId="14" pageNumber="215">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1248,1273]" pageId="14" pageNumber="215">Etymology.</emphasis>
The species epithet is derived from the Greek, 
<emphasis box="[860,915,1248,1273]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="215">pilos</emphasis>
(= hair), referring to hairy cilia of the antenna.
</paragraph>
